tter, the newly
reformatted and spruced-up =E2=80=98CBS Evening News=E2=80=99 seems to be a=
 quickly metastasizing ratings and formatting disaster=E2=80=94and the late=
st reminder that few things unite a newsroom quite like one of their boss=
=E2=80=99s public shortcomings.

